    Options: Object

    API client options object.

    Static Public

    public Options: Object source

    API client options object. Please use APIClient#options to get and set them.

    Properties:

    NameTypeAttributeDescription
    wsServer Object
    • optional

    WebSocket server configuration.
    wsServer.protocol String
    • optional
    • default: ws:

    WS protocol prefix.
    wsServer.hostname String
    • optional
    • default: localhost

    WS host name.
    wsServer.port Number
    • optional
    • default: 80

    WS host port.
    wsServer.prefixPath String
    • optional

    WS prefix path.
    wsServer.path String
    • optional
    • default: /websocket

    WS path.
    xhrServer Object
    • optional

    XHR server configuration.
    xhrServer.protocol String
    • optional
    • default: http:

    XHR protocol prefix.
    xhrServer.hostname String
    • optional
    • default: localhost

    XHR host name.
    xhrServer.port Number
    • optional
    • default: 80

    XHR host port.
    xhrServer.prefixPath String
    • optional

    XHR prefix path.
    primaryProtocol 'xhr' | 'ws'
    • optional
    • default: xhr

    Primary communication protocol.
    webSocketUpgrade Boolean
    • optional
    • default: true

    Whether the protocol can be upgraded to WebSocket.
    createWebSocket Function
    • optional

    Creates a WebSocket connection.
    packMessage Function
    • optional

    Pack the WebSocket message using JSON.
    unpackMessage Function
    • optional

    Unpack the WebSocket message using JSON.
    attachRequestId Function
    • optional

    Attach a request ID to every outgoing WebSocket message.
    extractRequestId Function
    • optional

    Extract the request ID from the WebSocket response.
    openTimeout Number
    • optional
    • default: 0

    Timeout for the opening of a WebSocket connection.
    closeTimeout Number
    • optional
    • default: 0

    Timeout for the closing of a WebSocket connection.
    responseTimeout Number
    • optional
    • default: 30000

    Timeout for the responses of WebSocket requests.
    pollingPushEventHandlerInterval Number
    • optional
    • default: 10000

    Interval for the polling of the push event messages (for the XHR fallback).
    refreshPushEventSubscriptionsTimeout Number
    • optional
    • default: 2000

    Timeut for the first refresh call of the push event subscriptions.
    refreshPushEventSubscriptionsInterval Number
    • optional
    • default: 60000

    Interval for the refresh of the push event subscriptions.
    reconnect Boolean
    • optional
    • default: true

    Defines if WebSocket connection should be automatically re-established on close.
    reconnectionDelayIncrement Number
    • optional
    • default: 1000

    Increment in delay with every reconnection attempt.
    maxReconnectionDelay Number
    • optional
    • default: 10000

    Maximum delay when trying to re-establish WebSocket connection.
    maxReconnectionAttempts Number
    • optional
    • default: 10

    Maximum number of attempts before giving up trying to re-establish a WebSocket connection.
    accessToken String
    • optional

    Access token to include in all requests where authentication is required.
    throwError Boolean
    • optional

    Throw errors when connection is not open (only for WS requests).
    isAppIdle Boolean
    • optional

    Idle state of the application, will be set to true if the user hasn't interacted with it in the configured time period.
